id":2111150,"uid":64922,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cf7ca6bc4a3f14f6902413674810386ed049c6b0","tid":2111150,"uid":20563,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"8c461f6e82add2e055061eefe46d2fc4fca89972","tid":2111150,"uid":254594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:53:28.000Z","msg":"但比人淘汰總有原因<br />\n淨係因為價錢無優勢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"定係日本仔民族性，自我放棄海外市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:27:34.000Z","msg":"支那屎為黨補貼<br />\n再加全球偷技術+強迫技術轉移<br />\n不公平競爭咪唔夠支那玩<br />\n屎為無得玩下大家公平競爭就唔同啦"},{"pid":"f97e6faf464fde08499d5c4eb4d3916136bfe64c","tid":2111150,"uid":171611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:30:16.000Z","msg":"NEC係日本電器公司中最垃圾，早期已經開始食老本"},{"pid":"be1b15a80b085ab41da9c8b57c248f90dab467d9","tid":2111150,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa915318a53fd4a320b85ee023f866198bfb6cc","tid":2111150,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"英國最新加入美國封殺華為5G設備的行列，其他通訊公司如Nokia、愛立信等則被認為有望填補市場空缺，而目前在全球無線網路基地台市場中，市佔率不到1%、被媒體稱為近乎「死亡」的日本資訊科技公司「日本電氣」（NEC），也看見在電信設備業再起的機會，該公司已和日本電信電話（NTT）在發展5G通訊上結盟，並加入了美國Open RAN政策聯盟（Open RAN Policy Coalition）。<br />\n<br />\n《日經新聞》今（16）報導，日本電氣在美國及其盟國封殺華為的趨勢下，正看見拓展市場的機會，該公司已和NTT在5G通訊建設上結盟，將獲得NTT投資645億日圓購入NEC近5％的股份，也和NTT一同加入在美國成立的Open RAN政策聯盟。<br />\n<br />\nNEC執行長Takashi Niino表示，該公司和NTT的聯盟，代表了日本在5G領域取得成功的「最後機會」。NTT高管則稱，美國政府直接要求該公司加入Open RAN政策聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，出於技術標準不一，要用多個供應商設備建設基地台非常困難，因此華為整合式的方案便具有優勢，而Open RAN政策聯盟，便旨在以無線網路的開放式架構，打破設備壟斷，不同供應商都可參與基地台建設，設備部署成本也有望因供應商多樣化而降低。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>目前Open RAN政策聯盟的知名成員，包括Google、微軟、臉書等知名美國企業。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3230425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3230425&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=62f364db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3230425&h=c856a843\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3230425</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:31:59.000Z","msg":"當年好威既3G機&hellip;c616&rsquo;"},{"pid":"7da5e147edb969c2a64d5a5d0eee15d6b4051586","tid":2111150,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"其實NEC無收皮，佢既人臉辦識技術係先進國家中最撚勁"},{"pid":"7fdb8d44e19f0dedd7af85086c13f851490a9814","tid":2111150,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f97e6faf464fde08499d5c4eb4d3916136bfe64c","tid":2111150,"uid":171611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:30:16.000Z","msg":"NEC係日本電器公司中最垃圾，早期已經開始食老本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:36:46.000Z","msg":"佢係日本有好多地、又有衛星技術專利大堆專利費野，乜都唔開發唔做都企到今日"},{"pid":"d1ad01884f93bec4bc098661210c74a6b626522a","tid":2111150,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4622218a8fe83edc1ab079f7e9ec295b0b63cb14","tid":2111150,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f4666f96f2a1a821a941a15f3187b5010b4322","tid":2111150,"uid":98289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd84b9bb8914524222b8d7ead810742adb01ba0c","tid":2111150,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"586a547bc43713828f24a0af20196a52fd825f29","tid":2111150,"uid":231583,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"瓜分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到好似一定係屎為咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-1